OL,5, Canadian prosecutors began laying out  
OL,6, arguments against former fashion mogul 
OL,7, Peter Nygard as his sexual assault     
OL,8, trial opened in an Ontario court.      
OL,10,FIn opening remarks, they alleged Mr    
OL,11,FNygard, 82, used his "power and status"
OL,12,Fto assault five women in incidents     
OL,13,Fdating from the late 1980s to 2005.    
OL,15,FHe lured the women - aged 16 to 28 at  
OL,16,Fthe time - into a private bedroom in   
OL,17,Fhis firm's Toronto headquarters,       
OL,18,Fprosecutors said.                      
OL,20,FMr Nygard has denied all the charges.  
